articles.title: Australia retain Ashes after rain plays spoilsport - ICC Cricket
articles.description: Rain washed out play on day five as Australia retained their 2-1 lead and ensured they would leave England shores with the Ashes intact.
articles.content: Rain washed out play on day five as Australia retained their 2-1 lead and ensured they would leave England shores with the Ashes intact.Rain washed away England's hopes of levelling the series on day… [+1701 chars]
